{"tid":129552,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（認真post)讀hkcc嘅巴絲們入一入黎","createTime":"2017-02-21T16:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T11:08:24.000Z","uid":66889,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f33347fd03a11c38cca71f6dc2b0da4544b171","tid":129552,"uid":66889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:20:44.000Z","msg":"小弟我就讀hkcc嘅，今年yr2,咁頭兩個sem就考得好差，拉低晒個gpa。咁今日我就同個tutor傾過，佢話可以withdraw一科搞到唔夠credit畢業去讀sem5,但係sem5只可以retake2科，加多一科withdraw左嘅，但係學校嗰邊唔一定批。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而我老母就好想小弟讀大學，水泡科都無咩所謂，我想問下各位巴絲搏唔搏得過？我sem1同2gpa都係2.6，sem3 3.4，拉出黎得2.87，如果今個sem keep著3.4就啱啱有3，retake2科當由c同c-升去b+，報水泡科係唔係會穩陣啲？<br />\n<br />\n因為我本身個人比較毒，無朋友，搵唔到人傾，唯有上黎開po問下大家意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家覺得我應該讀top up定搏下retake?同埋下個禮拜2有speed嗰邊嘅interview，我應唔應該去in左先？<br />\n<br />\n送上圖一張，證明無吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xGD14Qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGD14Qi.jpg&h=5d625aec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2aa31c915e4441ac626036da3a03c2f1f3ba7896","tid":129552,"uid":67008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:24:12.000Z","msg":"你有無諗過自己唔啱讀商科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高grade啲科同商科一啲關係都無"},{"pid":"103e716fe96a489b5bdd61cb37c767f00ee854c3","tid":129552,"uid":18968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有無諗過自己唔啱讀商科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高grade啲科同商科一啲關係都無</blockquote><br />\n同意"},{"pid":"bbab4aeeaf960ee9ab758661eca99a6616f5fd1a","tid":129552,"uid":66889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有無諗過自己唔啱讀商科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gi