\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過以商科嚟僅僅過3都好唔似唔算乜嘢好成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你咪試吓報吓啲水泡UGC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再加speed囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實speed都係學士啊，入到speed咪再試吓報U</blockquote><br />\n唉其實我原本諗著hkcc係學店，你肯retake佢一定收，所以差唔多咩都無報淨係報左speed,因為諗著既然retake就無謂晒錢報水泡科，我睇番連登non ju ugc個stat 啲水泡科都係cgpa3咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267f6f5faf2f76646b9b87cb6c878378ba918001","tid":129552,"uid":64558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係望到你sem4 d科已經為你擔心緊。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBtw如果我係你我會withdraw中西溝/food service再爆stat同jp2最好兩科A+晒之後sem5 retake番sem1既stat同fa上A/A+ 咁樣應該最易</blockquote><br />\nfa就一定retake,但係得2個quota retake sem1科數好咩，本身諗著retake econ。btw sem 1係咪唔開ia?</blockquote><br />\nSem1科數先最易A+，識人C+番A+都有"},{"pid":"dd02555e31f221882fcf9be71fd861ad1550ca5c","tid":129552,"uid":79469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:10:38.000Z","msg":"認真 不如砍掉重練啦"},{"pid":"801956eaf203ce4548088b729f55880cccfb8866","tid":129552,"uid":66889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T01:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真 不如砍掉重練啦</blockquote><br />\n其實有諗過quit cc重新讀過，但好似又晒多兩年咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169b939b66556f801b4ecd7f39d4d3ce9177d455","tid":129552,"uid":15206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T01:33:16.000Z","msg":"你跟本就唔適合讀business,就算上到degree,個gpa只會愈差，最後拎住個垃圾U既degree&amp;垃圾gpa都唔會搵到好工<br />\n<br />\n咁想讀u咪去speed囉，岩你呢d想做大學生既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be19ae41befb5c7dcacac68b0007dc1003b054d0","tid":129552,"uid":60020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T02:04: